gr_use 
How to use the generic randomizer.

  1. In your monster code, add this in the reset() function:               
          /players/Bad/Objects/generic_randomizer"->blah();             

     where blah() can be any of the functions defines in the gen. rand.    
     to remind you again, the functions in the gen. rand. are:             
          gimme_a_name()                                             
          gimme_an_adjective()                                             
          gimme_an_adj_phrase()                                            
          gimme_a_prof()                                            
          gimme_a_male_prof()                                            
          gimme_a_female_prof()                                            

  2. If you still are confused, read the help docs about the specific      
     functions.                                                            

